title: Amiga music: mA2E - Amazed by Pokey (A1200🎧Dolbyfied)
description:
"Amazed by Pokey" (2021) by mA2E/Desire (Stian Gudbrandsen). An Amiga cover of a track originally made for Atari XL/XE. Alternate A500 r6a version here https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H9C8n9ZlipQ
Art "Wielki las" by Aszu, 7th at RetroKomp/LOAD ERROR 2015.

Original version can be heard at Maze's channel:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Rx8BzwGbqmM

Made using real A1200 Rev. 1D.4 audio.

Visit my channel for more Amiga music.
